hopobject.body: I can't get through at the moment icaro.med.br/movimento11 A 120-pound woman smoked the competition Saturday, becoming the first of her sex to win the Kansas City area’s Bacon Fest eating contest. Molly Schuyler, a military wife and mother of four children, swallowed a pound of Farmland bacon in three minutes, beating out 20 contestants, mainly male, in the fifth annual Bacon Fest, a fundraiser for the Rehabilitation Institute of Kansas City, which helps recently disabled children and adults.
